faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.incimages.com/uploaded_files/image/1920x1080/getty_1130598318_411195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.incimages.com%2Fuploaded_files%2Fimage%2F1920x1080%2Fgetty_1130598318_411195.jpg&h=41c7d9ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:05:45.000Z","msg":"食屎吧大麻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:23:30.000Z","msg":"豬持樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界無可能只升不跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f3dfe34812d0fc7fc9c662cf8ccaf1e7069e76","tid":2357972,"uid":255650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:32:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2846472/%E3%80%90Tesla%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%91%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%EF%BC%9ATesla%E7%A9%BA%E5%80%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E8%9D%95%E9%80%BE3000%E5%84%84%E3%80%80%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2846472%2F%25E3%2580%2590Tesla%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2583%25B9%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25EF%25BC%259ATesla%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%2580%2589%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2599%25A7%25E8%259D%2595%25E9%2580%25BE3000%25E5%2584%2584%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=4321b19f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2846472/%E3%80%90Tesla%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%91%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%EF%BC%9ATesla%E7%A9%BA%E5%80%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E8%9D%95%E9%80%BE3000%E5%84%84%E3%80%80%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84</a><br />\n<br />\nTesla特斯拉（美：TSLA）幾乎完成2020年付運50萬架電動車，股價不斷破頂。Tesla股價2020年累升7倍﹐一方面令Tesla創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）身家漲至逾1000億美元，另一方面不時質疑Tesla 的看淡投資者受重創，金融數據公司S3 Partners分析，2020年Tesla淡倉投資者損失金額達401億美元（約3109億港元），單計12月已虧62.9億美元。<br />\n<br />\nS3 Partners董事總經理Ihor Dusaniwsky表示，這不單是2020年做淡任何股票的投資者遭受的最大損失，也是有史以來最大的空倉虧損。<br />\n<br />\n至1月4日，Tesla空倉規模約4422萬股或5.83%，時值312億美元，較市值大得多的蘋果公司（美：AAPL）約133億美元淡倉，明顯較多。蘋果公司的淡倉規模相當於已發行股本約0.6%。<br />\n<br />\nDusaniwsky指出，單計2021年交易至今，造淡Tesla的投資者再錄10.7億美元帳面虧損。<br />\n<br />\n沽空股票不一定是單邊造淡，也可能涉及對沖風險的需求，在急速上升的股份，淡倉規模一般較高。<br />\n<br />\nTesla 一直以來有不少「黑粉」，包括摩通分析師一直給予極低目標價。同樣多番質疑Tesla業務難持續的沽空機構渾水（Muddy Waters）創辦人Carson Block，去年中已稱沽空Tesla風險自付，他不會這樣做，「我沒有沽空這股票，感謝主。」"},{"pid":"b20ed896b16aba698a293c51aa54a458b45c8088","tid":2357972,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1477cae8cff3ea71b8b5cf67e0a5ec80a50503f0","tid":2357972,"uid":241507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4a37c7b0c11b0858cd321cedd14ceb08b30e3a","tid":2357972,"uid":16063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"777b60843c4f78de751d4c6499cb1d9c7f064055","tid":2357972,"uid":73095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"沽空 TSLA 沒有一個是無辜的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.incimages.com/uploaded_files/image/1920x1080/getty_1130598318_411195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.incimages.com%2Fuploaded_files%2Fimage%2F1920x1080%2Fgetty_1130598318_411195.jpg&h=41c7d9ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:05:45.000Z","msg":"食屎吧大麻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:23:30.000Z","msg":"豬持樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界無可能只升不跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:35:39.000Z","msg":"一齊沽撚爆佢<br />\n成班傻龍友最後狂歡 <br />\n一！齊！沽！到！佢！落！地！獄！"},{"pid":"2247be7a97202fa9fa167686209509fce61457a0","tid":2357972,"uid":30006,"