 />\n<br />\nS3 Partners董事總經理Ihor Dusaniwsky表示，這不單是2020年做淡任何股票的投資者遭受的最大損失，也是有史以來最大的空倉虧損。<br />\n<br />\n至1月4日，Tesla空倉規模約4422萬股或5.83%，時值312億美元，較市值大得多的蘋果公司（美：AAPL）約133億美元淡倉，明顯較多。蘋果公司的淡倉規模相當於已發行股本約0.6%。<br />\n<br />\nDusaniwsky指出，單計2021年交易至今，造淡Tesla的投資者再錄10.7億美元帳面虧損。<br />\n<br />\n沽空股票不一定是單邊造淡，也可能涉及對沖風險的需求，在急速上升的股份，淡倉規模一般較高。<br />\n<br />\nTesla 一直以來有不少「黑粉」，包括摩通分析師一直給予極低目標價。同樣多番質疑Tesla業務難持續的沽空機構渾水（Muddy Waters）創辦人Carson Block，去年中已稱沽空Tesla風險自付，他不會這樣做，「我沒有沽空這股票，感謝主。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:30:53.000Z","msg":"On9仔先沽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5777a957fc359c5f65592539fdfc46eb4ea6e42f","tid":2357972,"uid":109165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"560c6bd71edf0e4a413bb62a6305ac3326975305","tid":2357972,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T21:29:18.000Z","msg":"伊朗馬斯克食能屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇我沽爆你條大麻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍友食能屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:50:05.000Z","msg":"輸咗"},{"pid":"a9e2ca73813d86b5c032fcd128e35a6b5d3c7510","tid":2357972,"uid":241507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T22:56:10.000Z","msg":"收市後跌左0.11%<br />\n淡友之勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c202dcf5b75ca09f61869318c4372af9b087bbf","tid":2357972,"uid":12241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T23:10:19.000Z","msg":"呢隻股都幾神奇<br />\n兩年前買左萬幾蚊美金渣到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba4c2c480c4bf6eaa14f00184765b43b25117c9","tid":2357972,"uid":73095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e2ca73813d